  "detailed_description": "玩家将扮演小恶魔和帕秋莉解开重重谜团，躲避种种危机。<br><br>这不是一场异变，却比异变带来了更多关于友情与亲情的考验。<br>她们能否凿碎黑暗的笼罩，寻找到心的曙光？<br><br>……<br>那誓言如同光一样纯粹透明，<br>似乎能点亮一切黑暗,<br>我们相信着彼此，一如既往......<br><br>------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------<br><br>本作为东方Project的二次创作作品（同人游戏），是一部以解密和剧情为主的RM游戏。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >本游戏的特色</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/b21da6ea1b0d25f6c2abb181c3ff01c0.poster.avif?t=1667017263\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/b21da6ea1b0d25f6c2abb181c3ff01c0.webm?t=1667017263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/b21da6ea1b0d25f6c2abb181c3ff01c0.mp4?t=1667017263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在神秘的遗迹中解开层层迷题，探寻事件的真相<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/f4d8f36a825cab35d45ef270f6247690.poster.avif?t=1667017263\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/f4d8f36a825cab35d45ef270f6247690.webm?t=1667017263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/f4d8f36a825cab35d45ef270f6247690.mp4?t=1667017263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>在多条玩法各具特色的线路中操纵三位主角，达到不同的结局，合力解开命运的枷锁<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/8e00efe0bf56f7b1004d192db8f8c2a8.poster.avif?t=1667017263\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/8e00efe0bf56f7b1004d192db8f8c2a8.webm?t=1667017263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/8e00efe0bf56f7b1004d192db8f8c2a8.mp4?t=1667017263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>颠覆传统rpgmaker游戏的即时弹幕战斗系统，多种风格各异的boss等你来挑战<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/662a678db32091874885dcf7280a5b3e.poster.avif?t=1667017263\" width=640 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/662a678db32091874885dcf7280a5b3e.webm?t=1667017263\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015700/extras/662a678db32091874885dcf7280a5b3e.mp4?t=1667017263\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>丰富多彩的新奇小游戏玩法，让你耳目一新",
